text:
Ability to add custom web-components to blog post richtext without HubSpot removing them.
Example (when added to a RTF, it is automatically removed from the markup):
*NOTE: presently, the only place you can't insert WCs is inside of the blog post body.*

```&lt;quote-card attribute="value"&gt;
  &lt;h3 slot="quote"&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.&lt;/h3&gt;
  &lt;p slot="author"&gt;Lorem Ipsum&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/quote-card&gt;```
